        <span class="tag-badge">Coastal Villa</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h3>Sea-View Villa Living Pavilion</h3>
        <div class="location">📍 Kapu Beachfront · 3,800 sq ft</div>
        <p class="desc">Open-plan living pavilion with floor-to-ceiling glass, custom teak wood rafters, and natural slate accents designed for sea-breeze circulation.</p>
        <div class="materials-list">
          <span class="mat-chip">Burma Teak</span>
          <span class="mat-chip">Italian Travertine</span>
          <span class="mat-chip">Acoustic Glass</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-foot">
          <a href="/contact?service=interior&ref=Kapu-Villa" class="cta-btn">Enquire for This Design →</a>
        </div>
